			<div class = "work-description">
				<div class = "title"> <p>Granulator</p> </div>
				<p>
				Designed and programmed a granular delay plugin in C++ using the JUCE framework. 
				</p>
				<p>
				A real-time granular synthesis effect that chops up the input signal into tiny grains. User has access to settings that affect the buffer read position, pitch, duration, panning and volume of individual grains. The buffer can be frozen at any time.
				</p>
				<div class = "subtitle"> <p>Release: Sometime 2017 </p> </div>
